{
  "stem": "543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wouldn't be-- I-- I wouldn't be afraid to die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was afraid to die how-- that he hurt me, that I was, you know, if there's-- in pain or annoying pain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to die, just the dying wasn't mean-- they slapped-- you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I see their mind go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, the only thing what they always used to say to the-- in block 10 people-- there was never enough food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you're skinnier, and skinnier, and skinnier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there is not enough food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, then after the-- yeah, we-- we-- this is also a whole different story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I were a couple-- I mean, oh, couple of-- I-- I were a couple months in Auschwitz, in-- in the-- after three months there they call-- there comes the big trucks, and they take you away-- the people who are skinny, people who are sick, people who couldn't-- from the-- they get taked away.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was three times on a truck, and three times they took me off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They say I'm not finished with-- Mrs-- but you we never young.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- we have to work-- I was-- other thing I have to tell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was born with an-- a thyroid deficiency-- deficiency.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still get thyroid pills to the day, for today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I was six years old or seven year old, they find out I had a thyroid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I get thyroid pill still every day now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I get every morning a thyroid pill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I can live with little food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm worried the fatter I get.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't work it off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't burn it off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- with all the people walking around a skeleton, I looked pretty good.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
